Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.519
Route 53 is AWSs cloud Domain Name System Service.

00:00:05.519 --> 00:00:09.285
Route 53 is a reliable and scalable service

00:00:09.285 --> 00:00:12.855
that has DNS servers distributed around the globe.

00:00:12.855 --> 00:00:18.763
Route 53 scales automatically to manage spikes in DNS queries,

00:00:18.763 --> 00:00:23.539
allows you to register a domain name or managed and existing one.

00:00:23.539 --> 00:00:26.629
Route's internet traffic to the resources for

00:00:26.629 --> 00:00:30.695
your domain and checks the health of your resources.

00:00:30.695 --> 00:00:33.590
The health checks are useful because they help to

00:00:33.590 --> 00:00:37.430
ensure that your web servers are up and running and offer

00:00:37.429 --> 00:00:40.039
DNS failover to automatically route

00:00:40.039 --> 00:00:45.570
your web visitors to an alternate location to avoid site outages.

